#. Marquez. Macondo is a fictional place where magic and reality are mixed.
#. TRANSLATORS: https://iau.org/news/pressreleases/detail/iau1912/
msgid "Macondo"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Proper name of star HD 221287
