#. TRANSLATORS: https://iau.org/news/pressreleases/detail/iau1912/
msgid "Aniara"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Proper name of star HD 130322
#. TRANSLATORS: Mönch is one of the prominent peaks of the Bernese Alps in
